so go easy, darling.

26
00:05:47,427 --> 00:05:48,655
Yes ma'am.

27
00:06:05,845 --> 00:06:08,370
(panting)

28
00:06:30,103 --> 00:06:32,435
- Thanks, Vera.
- You're welcome.

29
00:06:32,505 --> 00:06:33,767
Yeah.

30
00:06:53,893 --> 00:06:56,157
What's the matter, hon?
You look so sad.

31
00:06:57,597 --> 00:06:59,030
Sonny: I'm fine.

32
00:06:59,099 --> 00:07:00,589
Hey?

33
00:07:02,602 --> 00:07:04,593
