- Talk?
- Take care, Sonny.

35
00:07:28,795 --> 00:07:31,525
(folk music playing)

36
00:07:39,706 --> 00:07:41,367
Morning, Pop.

37
00:07:43,943 --> 00:07:46,207
This shit's cold.
I'm gonna get some more.

38
00:08:26,119 --> 00:08:28,553
Pop: What the hell are
those niggers doing out there?

39
00:08:31,057 --> 00:08:33,423
I said something to you.
Did you hear me?

40
00:08:35,795 --> 00:08:37,285
Yeah.

41
00:08:37,363 --> 00:08:41,527
Damn porch monkeys.
Be moving in here soon.

42
00:08:43,036 --> 00:08:47,302
Sitting next to me...
watching my TV.

43
00:08:49,709 --> 00:08:52,041
There was a time
when they knew their place.

44
00:08:53,580 --> 00:08:56,310
Wasn't none of this
mixing going on.

45
00:09:03,723 --> 00:09:06,157
Your mother,
she hated them niggers, too.

46
00:09:18,771 --> 00:09:20,898
Tell them to get
the hell off my property.

47
00:09:22,609 --> 00:09:25,203
- You put that thing down.
- Boy: We came by to see Sonny.

48
00:09:25,278 --> 00:09:27,212
I don't give a damn
who you come by to see.

49
00:09:27,280 --> 00:09:28,975
Get them out of here
right now.

50
00:09:29,048 --> 00:09:31,539
